@HostAddress = http://localhost:5069

###4. Start NEW Game Session (Fresh Test)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/Game/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "module_id": "20000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001"
}

### 5. Submit Answer - NEW Question (Correct)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/Game/6c85a78b-2f2b-4ff7-a93f-a00b5cb9262e/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_id": "6342ee8a-67f1-4982-b179-3339871a7b80",
  "user_answer": "Paris",
  "time_taken_seconds": 8
}

### 6. Submit Answer - NEW Question (Wrong)
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/Game/6c85a78b-2f2b-4ff7-a93f-a00b5cb9262e/answer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question_id": "6342ee8a-67f1-4982-b179-3339871a7b80",
  "user_answer": "London",
  "time_taken_seconds": 12
}

### 7. End NEW Game Session
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/Game/6c85a78b-2f2b-4ff7-a93f-a00b5cb9262e/end